node.title: Three killed in crashes this weekend
node.description: Three people have been killed in crashes this weekend, in Auckland, north of Auckland, and Canterbury.
node.content:
["Three people have been killed in crashes this weekend, in Auckland, north of Auckland, and Canterbury.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf\n
", "This morning police said one person had died after a crash at Te Arai, near Mangawhai, north of Auckland.", "Ocean View Road has been closed while emergency services work at the scene.", "In a statement, police said only one vehicle was involved.", "Diversions are in place, but motorists should avoid the area.", "In Auckland a cyclist has died after being hit by a truck on Manukau Road in Royal Oak late yesterday morning.", "Another person was killed in a crash on the outskirts of Ashburton in Canterbury yesterday afternoon.", "The crash happened on Beach Road East in Elgin."]
